result.name: Chung Hing Restaurant

reviews.text:
This my first time visit this nice restaurant .one of my introduce to me he said it's one the best tea time options (tea time the prices is disconnected )
I order fresh squids soy bean and green paper with Hong Kong coffee style 
The food was good 
The furniture and design it's very Chinese style .made the environment looks so Chinese 
I love it personally 
Waiters are helpful and nice
Siu mei is good.
Ok
Good place to carb up since they give you a large serving of rice/noodles. Food is average, price is reasonable taking into account the location.
